<< /Length 685 >>
stream
BT
/F1 11 Tf
50 790 Td
14 TL
(Module 3 - Work, Energy, Power and Heat) Tj
T*
(Work W = Fs cos theta. Work is zero if displacement is zero.) Tj
T*
(Friction f = mu R. Reduce friction using lubrication, polishing, ball bearings and) Tj
T*
(streamlining.) Tj
T*
(Kinetic energy KE = 1/2 mv^2. Potential energy PE = mgh. Energy is transformed, not) Tj
T*
(destroyed.) Tj
T*
(Power P = W/t = Fv. Unit is watt.) Tj
T*
(Temperature conversion: K = C + 273; F = 9C/5 + 32. Heat Q = mc Delta T.) Tj
T*
(Heat transfer: conduction in solids, convection in fluids and radiation without medium.) Tj
T*
(Mercury thermometer uses expansion; pyrometer measures high temperature without contact.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
6 0 obj
<< /Length 775 >>
stream
BT
/F1 11 Tf
50 790 Td
14 TL
(Module 4 - Elasticity, Pressure and Fluids) Tj
T*
(Elasticity: body regains original shape after removing deforming force. Stress = F/A.) Tj
T*
(Strain = change/original. Young modulus Y = stress/strain.) Tj
T*
(Pressure P = F/A. Absolute pressure = atmospheric pressure + gauge pressure.) Tj
T*
(Surface tension T = force/length. Capillary rise h = 2T cos theta/\(rho g r\). Detergents) Tj
T*
(reduce surface tension.) Tj
T*
(Viscosity is resistance between fluid layers. Stokes law: F = 6 pi eta r v.) Tj
T*
(Reynolds number Re = rho vD/eta. Low Re: streamline flow; high Re: turbulent flow.) Tj
T*
(Continuity equation: A1v1 = A2v2. Bernoulli: P + 1/2 rho v^2 + rho gh = constant.) Tj
T*
(Applications: airfoil, atomiser, venturimeter.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
